title: [A Canted Wagon]
description: The wagon straddles the edge of some subsurface rock, tipping it awkwardly to one side.  Sucking sounds from the noisome muck indicate the process is on-going.  With its axles leaning to within a hand's breadth of the mire's surface, the wagon looks as though it is being slowly devoured by the swamp.
